{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"MathML attribute reference","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>此页面是 MathML 属性的字母表。 每个属性的更多详细信息请看这里<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Element\">element pages</a>。</p>\n\n<p>注意：</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li>MathML 的 <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code> 和 <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code> 元素接受所有&nbsp;MathML 的描述元素。</li>\n <li>请参阅 MathML 中值（<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Attributes/Values\">values</a>）和单位的注释值。</li>\n</ul>\n\n<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th>名（Name）</th>\n   <th>元素接受的属性（Elements accepting attribute）</th>\n   <th>描述（Description）</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr id=\"accent\">\n   <td><code>accent</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mover&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>布尔类型的值，指明操作符是否应该被视为 accent。</p>\n\n    <p>原文：A Boolean value specifying whether the operator should be treated as an accent.</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"accentunder\">\n   <td><code>accentunder</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munder&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>\n    <p>布尔类型的值，指明操作符是否应该被视为 accent。</p>\n\n    <p>原文：A Boolean value specifying whether the operator should be treated as an accent.</p>\n   </td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"actiontype\">\n   <td><code>actiontype</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\" title=\"<maction>\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>字符串类型的值，指明元素发生的操作。</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"align\">\n   <td><code>align</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code><br>\n    <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munder\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munder&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mover&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/munderover\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;munderover&gt; (en-US)</a></code><br>\n    <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies different alignments of several elements (see element pages for details).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"alignmentscope\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>alignmentscope</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value specifying whether table columns should act as alignment scopes or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"alt-*\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span><br>\n    <code>altimg</code><br>\n    <code>altimg-width</code><br>\n    <code>altimg-height</code><br>\n    <code>altimg-valign</code><br>\n    <code>alttext</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Visual and textual fall-back options.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"bevelled\">\n   <td><code>bevelled</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfrac&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the style how the fraction should be displayed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"charalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>charalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the horizontal alignment of digits.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"close\">\n   <td><code>close</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfenced&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A string for the closing delimiter.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnalign\">\n   <td><code>columnalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtd&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtr&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlabeledtr\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlabeledtr&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the horizontal alignment of table cells.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnlines\">\n   <td><code>columnlines</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies table column borders.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnspacing\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>columnspacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the space between table columns.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnspan\">\n   <td><code>columnspan</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtd&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A non-negative integer value that indicates on how many table columns does the cell extend.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"columnwidth\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>columnwidth</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the width of table columns.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"crossout\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>crossout</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarry\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarry&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies what kind of line is drawn to cross out carries.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"decimalpoint\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>decimalpoint</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>If the <code>decimalpoint</code> value is used to specify the <a href=\"#align\">alignment</a>, this attribute is specifying the character for the alignment point within <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code> and <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code> columns.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"denomalign\">\n   <td><code>denomalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfrac&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The alignment of the denominator under the fraction.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"depth\">\n   <td><code>depth</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Sets or increments the depth. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Attributes/Values\">length</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"dir\">\n   <td><code>dir</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mi&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mrow\" title=\"<mrow>\">&lt;mrow&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtext&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The text direction. Possible values are either ltr (left to right) or rtl (right to left).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"display\">\n   <td><code>display</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the rendering mode. The values <code>block</code> and <code>inline</code> are allowed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"displaystyle\">\n   <td><code>displaystyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value specifying whether more vertical space is used for displayed equations or, if set to <code>false</code>, a more compact layout is used to display formulas.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"edge\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>edge</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/malignmark\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;malignmark&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"equalcolumns\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>equalcolumns</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value indicating whether to force all columns to have the same total height.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"equalrows\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>equalrows</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value indicating whether to force all rows to have the same total height.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"fence\">\n   <td><code>fence</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A Boolean value specifying whether the operator is a fence (such as parentheses). There is no visual effect for this attribute.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"form\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>form</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the role of the operator in an enclosed expression.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"frame\">\n   <td><code>frame</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies borders of an entire <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code>. Possible values are: <code>none</code> (default), <code>solid</code> and <code>dashed</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"framespacing\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>framespacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies additional space added between the table and <code>frame</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"groupalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>groupalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maligngroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;maligngroup&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtd&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtr&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"height\">\n   <td><code>height</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the desired height. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Attributes/Values#Lengths\">lengths</a> for possible values.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"href\">\n   <td><code>href</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>Used to set a hyperlink to a specified URI.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"id\">\n   <td><code>id</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>Sets up a unique identifier associated with the element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indentalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentalignfirst\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indentalignfirst</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentalignlast\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indentalignlast</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentshift\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indentshift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentshiftfirst\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indentshiftfirst</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indentshiftlast\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indentshiftlast</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"indenttarget\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>indenttarget</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"infixlinebreakstyle\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>infixlinebreakstyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the default <code>linebreakstyle</code> to use for infix operators.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"largeop\">\n   <td><code>largeop</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies whether the operator should be drawn larger than normal.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"length\">\n   <td><code>length</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msline\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msline&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linebreak\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>linebreak</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linebreakmultchar\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>linebreakmultchar</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linebreakstyle\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>linebreakstyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"lineleading\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>lineleading</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"linethickness\">\n   <td><code>linethickness</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfrac&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The thickness of the horizontal fraction line.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"location\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>location</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarries\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarries&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"longdivstyle\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>longdivstyle</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlongdiv\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlongdiv&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Controls the style of the long division layout.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"lspace\">\n   <td><code>lspace</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The amount of space before the operator (see <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Attributes/Values#Lengths\">length</a> for values and units).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"lquote\">\n   <td><code>lquote</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The opening quote character (depends on <code>dir</code>) to enclose the content. The default value is \"<code>&amp;quot;</code>\".</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathbackground\">\n   <td><code>mathbackground</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>The background color. You can use <code>#rgb</code>, <code>#rrggbb</code> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#html.2fsvg.2fx11.c2.a0_color_keywords\" title=\"/en-US/docs/CSS/color_value#HTML.2fSVG.2fX11.c2.a0_Color_Keywords\">HTML color names</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathcolor\">\n   <td><code>mathcolor</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>The text color. You can use <code>#rgb</code>, <code>#rrggbb</code> and <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/color_value#html.2fsvg.2fx11.c2.a0_color_keywords\" title=\"/en-US/docs/CSS/color_value#HTML.2fSVG.2fX11.c2.a0_Color_Keywords\">HTML color names</a>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathsize\">\n   <td><code>mathsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mi&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mn&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtext&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The size of the content. Starting with Gecko 20.0 (Firefox 20 / Thunderbird 20 / SeaMonkey 2.17) unitless values are allowed and are interpreted as N times of the default size.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"mathvariant\">\n   <td><code>mathvariant</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mi\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mi&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mn\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mn&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtext\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtext&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The logical class of the identifier, which varies in typography.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"maxsize\">\n   <td><code>maxsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The maximum size of the operator.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"minlabelspacing\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>minlabelspacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Attributes/Values\">length value</a> specifing the minimum space between a <a href=\"Element/mlabeledtr\" rel=\"internal\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Element/mlabeledtr\">label</a> and the adjacent cell in the row.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"minsize\">\n   <td><code>minsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The minimum size of the operator.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"movablelimits\">\n   <td><code>movablelimits</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies whether attached under- and overscripts move to sub- and superscript positions.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"notation\">\n   <td><code>notation</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/menclose\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;menclose&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A list of notations, separated by white space, to apply to the child elements.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"numalign\">\n   <td><code>numalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfrac\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfrac&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The alignment of the numerator over the fraction.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"open\">\n   <td><code>open</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfenced&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A string for the opening delimiter.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"overflow\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>overflow</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>If an expression is too long to fit in the allowed width, this attribute sets the preferred handling.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"position\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>position</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msgroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msgroup&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msrow\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msrow&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mscarries\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mscarries&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msline\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msline&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowalign\">\n   <td><code>rowalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtd&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtr\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtr&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the vertical alignment of table cells.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowlines\">\n   <td><code>rowlines</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies table row borders.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowspacing\">\n   <td><code>rowspacing</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the space between table rows.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rowspan\">\n   <td><code>rowspan</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtd\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtd&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A non-negative integer value that indicates on how many rows does the cell extend.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rspace\">\n   <td><code>rspace</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The amount of space after the operator.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"rquote\">\n   <td><code>rquote</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/ms\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;ms&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>The closing quote mark (depends on <code>dir</code>) to enclose the content. The default value is \"<code>&amp;quot;</code>\".</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"scriptlevel\">\n   <td><code>scriptlevel</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Controls mostly the font-size. The higher the <code>scriptlevel</code>, the smaller the font size.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"scriptminsize\">\n   <td><code>scriptminsize</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies a minimum font size allowed due to changes in <code>scriptlevel</code>.<br>\n    Starting with Gecko 20.0 (Firefox 20 / Thunderbird 20 / SeaMonkey 2.17) unitless values and percent values are allowed and interpreted as multiple of \"8pt\".</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"scriptsizemultiplier\">\n   <td><code>scriptsizemultiplier</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstyle\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mstyle&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the multiplier to be used to adjust font size due to changes in <code>scriptlevel</code>.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"selection\">\n   <td><code>selection</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/maction\" title=\"<maction>\">&lt;maction&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The child element which is addressed by the action.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"separator\">\n   <td><code>separator</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>There is no visual effect for this attribute, but it specifies whether the operator is a separator (such as commas).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"separators\">\n   <td><code>separators</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mfenced\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mfenced&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>A sequence of zero or more characters to be used for different separators.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"shift\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>shift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msgroup\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;msgroup&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"side\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>side</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the position where <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mlabeledtr\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mlabeledtr&gt;</a></code> label elements should be placed.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"src\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>src</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The location of the image resource.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"stackalign\">\n   <td><span class=\"notecard inline warning\">未实现</span> <code>stackalign</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mstack\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mstack&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>&nbsp;</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"stretchy\">\n   <td><code>stretchy</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies whether the operator stretches to the size of the adjacent element.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"subscriptshift\">\n   <td><code>subscriptshift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msub\" title=\"<msub>\">&lt;msub&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"<msubsup>\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The minimum space by which to shift the subscript below the baseline of the expression.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"supscriptshift\">\n   <td><code>supscriptshift</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mmultiscripts\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mmultiscripts&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msup\" title=\"<msup>\">&lt;msup&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/msubsup\" title=\"<msubsup>\">&lt;msubsup&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>The minimum space by which to shift the superscript above the baseline of the expression.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"symmetric\">\n   <td><code>symmetric</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mo\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mo&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>If <code>stretchy</code> is <code>true</code>, this attribute specifies whether the operator should be vertically symmetric around the imaginary math axis (centered fraction line).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"voffset\">\n   <td><code>voffset</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Sets the vertical position of the child content.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"width\">\n   <td><code>width</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mglyph\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">&lt;mglyph&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mpadded\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mpadded&gt; (en-US)</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mspace\" title=\"<mspace>\">&lt;mspace&gt;</a></code>, <code><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Element/mtable\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" class=\"only-in-en-us\">&lt;mtable&gt; (en-US)</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the desired width. See <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute/Values#lengths\" title=\"/en-US/docs/MathML/Attributes/Values#Lengths\">lengths</a> for possible values.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"xlink-href\">\n   <td><code>xlink:href</code></td>\n   <td><em>All</em></td>\n   <td>Can be used to set a hyperlink to a specfied URI. However, authors are encouraged to use the <code>href</code> attribute instead.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr id=\"xmlns\">\n   <td><code>xmlns</code></td>\n   <td><code><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Element/math\" title=\"<math>\">&lt;math&gt;</a></code></td>\n   <td>Specifies the URI for the MathML namespace (<code><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\" rel=\"freelink noopener\">http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML</a></code>)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"此页面是 MathML 属性的字母表。 每个属性的更多详细信息请看这里element pages。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"MathML Attribut-Referenz","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"MathML attribute reference","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"MathML attribute reference","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Référence des attributs MathML","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"MathML 属性リファレンス","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Справка по атрибутам MathML","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/mathml/attribute","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/mathml/attribute/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML","title":"MathML"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/MathML/Attribute","title":"MathML attribute reference"}],"pageTitle":"MathML attribute reference - MathML | MDN","noIndexing":false}}